# Keep: build/aggregate/eval scripts, carve meta JSONs, result JSONs, smoke
# self-tests, aggregate_pareto.json. Exclude: bulky reproducible logs, pids,
# wandb run dir, inspect logs, and local draft PR-comment markdown.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
wandb/
# raw inspect_ai eval logs (reproducible, ~MB each)
_inspect_logs/
# verbose driver / server / chain stdout (progress bars; result JSONs hold the numbers)
_run_*.log
_server_*.log
_chain_*.log
# background-process pidfiles
*.pid
# local drafts of posted PR comments (the comments themselves live on the PR)
_pr_comment.md
_liveness_comment.md
